      "content": "Good evening \u00e2\u009d\u00a4\u00ef\u00b8\u008f\u00f0\u009f\u0090\u00bc, we do take on finger tattoos, however, we\u00e2\u0080\u0099d like to inform you that due to the unique nature of the skin in that area, the longevity of the result cannot be guaranteed. In some cases, the tattoo may fade or lose parts of the design even within a few days, as it is affected by factors such as friction and the healing process.\n\nGetting a tattoo on the fingers is done at your own discretion, and if a touch-up session is needed after 20 days. We just want you to be fully informed before proceeding, so you have realistic expectations. We\u00e2\u0080\u0099re here for any questions you may have!",
